### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST LOGOUT & PHÂN QUYỀN - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@cashierToken = 
@managerToken = 
@refreshToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. TEST LOGOUT
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin để lấy Token
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Logout thành công
# Sử dụng token từ response trên
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 1.3 Verify - Refresh Token sau Logout (Expected: 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 1.4 Logout không có Token (Expected: 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout

### 1.5 Logout với Token sai (Expected: 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

### ============================================
### 👤 2. TEST PHÂN QUYỀN - ADMIN
### ============================================

### 2.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 2.2 Admin - Get Users (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Get Products (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 💰 3. TEST PHÂN QUYỀN - CASHIER
### ============================================

### 3.1 Register Cashier mới
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Cashier",
  "username": "testcashier",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "confirmPassword": "Test@123",
  "role": "Cashier"
}

### 3.2 Login Cashier
# @name loginCashier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testcashier",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### 3.3 Cashier - Get Users (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 3.4 Cashier - Get Products (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 3.5 Cashier - Delete Product (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### ============================================
### 🧑‍💼 4. TEST PHÂN QUYỀN - MANAGER
### ============================================

### 4.1 Register Manager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Manager",
  "username": "testmanager",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "confirmPassword": "Test@123",
  "role": "Manager"
}

### 4.2 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testmanager",
  "password": "Test@123"
}

### 4.3 Manager - Get Products (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 4.4 Manager - Get Users (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### ❌ 5. TEST KHÔNG TOKEN
### ============================================

### 5.1 Get Users không token (Expected: 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### 5.2 Get Products không token (Expected: 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### ============================================
### 🔍 6. TEST KIỂM TRA THÔNG TIN USER
### ============================================

### 6.1 Get Current User Info (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.2 Get Current User Info (Cashier)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### ============================================
### 🛍️ 7. TEST PRODUCTS API - PHÂN QUYỀN
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Get All Products (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.2 Admin - Create Product (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Test Product Admin",
  "description": "Product created by admin",
  "price": 15000,
  "costPrice": 10000,
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "unit": "pcs",
  "barcode": "ADMIN001"
}

### 7.3 Cashier - Get All Products (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 7.4 Cashier - Create Product (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

{
  "name": "Test Product Cashier",
  "description": "Product created by cashier",
  "price": 10000,
  "costPrice": 5000,
  "stockQuantity": 20,
  "unit": "pcs",
  "barcode": "CASHIER001"
}

### 7.5 Cashier - Delete Product (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{cashierToken}}

### 7.6 Manager - Get Products (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 7.7 Manager - Create Product (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "name": "Test Product Manager",
  "description": "Product created by manager",
  "price": 20000,
  "costPrice": 12000,
  "stockQuantity": 30,
  "unit": "pcs",
  "barcode": "MANAGER001"
}

### 7.8 Search Products (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search?keyword=Test
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.9 Get Low Stock Products (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/low-stock?threshold=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Mở file này trong VS Code
### 3. Click "Send Request" bên trên mỗi request
### 4. Copy token từ response và paste vào biến @token
###
### LƯU Ý: 
### - Chạy từng request theo thứ tự
### - Copy token từ response và cập nhật biến @token
### - Kiểm tra kết quả expected ở mỗi request
###
### ============================================
### ✅ CHECKLIST TEST
### ============================================
### 
### LOGOUT:
### [ ] Login thành công
### [ ] Logout thành công với token hợp lệ
### [ ] Refresh token bị thu hồi sau logout
### [ ] Logout không có token → 401
### [ ] Logout với token sai → 401
###
### PHÂN QUYỀN:
### [ ] Admin → Get Users → 200 OK
### [ ] Admin → Get Products → 200 OK
### [ ] Cashier → Get Users → 403 Forbidden
### [ ] Cashier → Get Products → 200 OK
### [ ] Cashier → Create Product → 403 Forbidden
### [ ] Manager → Get Products → 200 OK
### [ ] Manager → Create Product → 200 OK
### [ ] No Token → Any API → 401 Unauthorized
###
